<form  class="cmxform frm" data-form="captivate">
    <div class="box-field">
        <input type="text" name="txtName" id="txtName" class="text-field" placeholder="Name This Connection" value="Captivate"  required>
        <i class="fas fa-podcast icon-field"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="box-field">
        <input type="text" name="txtUserId" id="txtUserId" class="text-field" placeholder="User ID" required>
        <i class="fas fa-plug icon-field"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="box-field">
        <input type="text" name="txtApiKey" id="txtApiKey" class="text-field" placeholder="Api Key" required>
        <i class="fas fa-key icon-field"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="box-field"><p>
        How To Get Your Captivate.fm User ID and API Key:<p>

            1. Visit the <a href="https://my.captivate.fm/dashboard/account/1/api" target="blank">My Account</a> page of your Captivate.fm account<p>
            
            Click on the "Reveal API key"<p>
            
            Copy "User ID" and "API Key", then Paste that into the Captivate User ID and API Key box above and click Connect.

    </div>

    <button class="btn btn-primary btnRetryConnection">
        <i class="fas fa-hand-o-left" aria-hidden="true"></i> Back
    </button>
    <button class="btn btn-success btnConnect">
        <i class="fas fa-podcast" aria-hidden="true"></i> Connect
    </button>
</form>
